### Login Success Detection
Login success can be verified by checking if the current URL no longer contains `sign_in`.

## Best Practices
- Use `page.waitForTimeout(3000)` after form submission to allow navigation
- Inspect page elements with `page.$$('input')` if selectors are unclear
